</li>
<li id="cite_note-12"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-12">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1133582631"><cite id="CITEREFWiegand,_Wayne_A.1979" class="citation book cs1"><a href="/wiki/Wayne_A._Wiegand" title="Wayne A. Wiegand">Wiegand, Wayne A.</a> (1979). <i>The History of a Hoax: Edmund Lester Pearson, John Cotton Dana, and the Old Librarian's Almanack</i>. Beta Phi Mu.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+History+of+a+Hoax%3A+Edmund+Lester+Pearson%2C+John+Cotton+Dana%2C+and+the+Old+Librarian%27s+Almanack.&amp;rft.pub=Beta+Phi+Mu&amp;rft.date=1979&amp;rft.au=Wiegand%2C+Wayne+A.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABook+curse" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-13"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1133582631"><cite id="CITEREFDanaKent1909" class="citation book cs1">Dana, John Cotton; Kent, Henry W. (1909). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=mdp.39015008605324"><i>The Old Librarian's Almanack</i></a><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2021-08-03</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Old+Librarian%27s+Almanack&amp;rft.date=1909&amp;rft.aulast=Dana&amp;rft.aufirst=John+Cotton&amp;rft.au=Kent%2C+Henry+W.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbabel.hathitrust.org%2Fcgi%2Fpt%3Fid%3Dmdp.39015008605324&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABook+curse" class="Z3988"></span> The hoax curse is on page 27.</span>
</li>
